"다른 <a href=\"//archive.org/projects/\">프로젝트</a>로는 <a "
"href=\"//archive.org/web/\">Wayback Machine</a>, <a "
"href=\"//archive.org/\">archive.org</a>, <a href=\"//archive-it.org"
"\">archive-it.org</a>가 있습니다."

